<!--<h4>First Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī śakavaruṣaṁbulu 1203 
<lb n="2"/>gunēṁṭi Uttarāyaṇa saṁkrāṁtti ni 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>mittamuna śrī voṁgōlini śrībhōgīśvara 
<lb n="4"/>śrīmanmahādēvara mukha maṁḍḍapamu 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>naku kannamareḍḍi tammireḍḍi tamataṁ 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ḍri kāmireḍḍiki tama talli māramaku 
<lb n="7"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> reḍḍisāniki dharmmavugāṁ beṁṭṭina 
<lb n="8"/>kaṁbhamu Ācaṁdrārkkasthāyigā śrī 
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="9"/>peṭṭina mōdā 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>lu 15 <unclear>vī</unclear>niṁjē 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>vārunamu <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> <unclear>pama</unclear> 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>valnānatāmu 
<lb n="13"/>peyavanaka 
<lb n="14" break="no"/>na 1 kāsenu 
<lb n="15"/>Ācaṁdrārkkaṁmu 
<lb n="16"/>Acuvāru 
<lb n="17" break="no"/>valnasēnu sella <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
</p>

